{"tid":1665632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1020一位路人甲分享","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:39:22.000Z","uid":299639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"642bbadc63f98ca149302c9e8e907a24ff4e16ad","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"朋友MSG分享<br />\n1. 下午有疑似炸彈時黑警同市民都雞飛狗走，黑警搞咗一輪再叫埋拆彈機器人出來先搞掂<br />\n呢D<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁危險O既疑似炸彈就千祈唔好再整</span></strong>  搞到黑警跪低晒冇得追示威者就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n2. 今日又係警車水炮車大巡遊，大大話話2、30架出晒啦  然後一行過玻璃碎時又要慢駛<br />\n似乎都係警整爆胎  所以下次<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有D 尖O既、會吉爆車胎O既雜物就咪留係馬路</span></strong> 免得又整爆Popo D 車胎啦<br />\n唔係<br />\n<br />\n3. 有路人唔知要跳繩定點  竟然係馬路拉繩 仲要有D拉係膝頭位 有D拉攔腰位 差D搞到Popo PK 又係個句<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 千祈唔好係馬路拉繩 </span></strong>仲要拉係D絆腳位"},{"pid":"eee8aa1cb4019b48b7c8d78e1dbeac6c06ffcf22","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"27e33c5763173d0bd01065f6c95ec422f828956e","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"f9d007049e31c18625e5061f6b0b08afd44eb588","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"309e493bad3715e4ce42e1b8913457cd6039aa4d","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"fb1cfb2f31736a8709e49d38863dec2c68bbfdc5","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:45:37.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"cbc51d0a9cedd8fc0bf196962c4504cb10ceb113","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下"},{"pid":"00e1692824d25deacf5c0e76a21137c3c2fa908e","tid":1665632,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike